---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact — LocalResizer" description="Get in touch with the LocalResizer team.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p>Have questions, feedback, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@localresizer.com">hello@localresizer.com</a></p>
    <h2>Report a Bug</h2>
    <p>Found something not working? Please include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your browser name and version</li>
      <li>The page URL where the issue occurred</li>
      <li>A brief description of what happened</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Feature Requests</h2>
    <p>We're always looking to improve. Let us know what features you'd like to see.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
